name: NewYearGreetings
0:
”Alexa start new year messages and suggest a new year wish”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: new year messages
des: Every year users greet "happy new year" in the same boring way. This skill provides users with around 200 different types of new year wishes. This skill can be invoked using command- "Alexa start new year messages and suggest me a new year wish".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
